EN: This country is worried about foreign invasion.

ZH: 侵略者在黄昏时分入侵了这座城市。
EN: The invaders invaded this city at dusk.

ZH: 珍妮从未忘记过那次侵略她家园的经历。
EN: Jenny has never forgotten the experience of her homeland being invaded.

ZH: 他们想要侵略我们的国土。
EN: They want to invade our land.

ZH: 侵略者不料遭到了顽强的抵抗。
EN: The invaders encountered strong resistance unexpectedly.

ZH: 在历史上，很多国家曾经成为过侵略者。
EN: Throughout history, many countries have been aggressors.

ZH: 战争引发了侵略和压迫。
EN: War leads to invasion and oppression.

ZH: 这部电影描述了一次外星侵略地球的情节。
EN: This movie depicts a plot where aliens invade Earth.

