EN: That nation has been resisting invaders.

ZH: 侵略不应该被视为一个解决问题的方法。
EN: Invasion should not be seen as a way to solve problems.

ZH: 这个帝国一直在扩张侵略领土。
EN: The empire has been expanding its territorial aggression.

ZH: 他讨厌那些试图侵略他家园的人。
EN: He hates those who try to invade his homeland.

