EN: This invasion brought economic hardships to the country.

ZH: 要求军队准备应对可能的侵略威胁。
EN: The army is asked to prepare for potential invasion threats.

ZH: 不顾一切的侵略行为将导致严重后果。
EN: Reckless acts of aggression will lead to serious consequences.
